  • Method Details

    • execute

      public void execute(List<String> input) throws NoFileOpenedException, WrongArgumentsCountException
      Gets the specified planet from the PlanetsRepository, gets the strongest jedi on that planet via the JediStatisticsService.getYoungestJediOfRankOnPlanet(Rank, Planet) method and displays the information about them using Jedi.toString() implicitly. If the specified planet does not exist (PlanetDoesNotExistException), the supplied value for rank is invalid (InvalidRankException) or there are no jedi of the specified rank on the given planet (NoJediOfThisRankOnPlanetException), an appropriate error message is displayed.
      Specified by:
      execute in interface Command
      Parameters:
      input - the user input.
      Throws:
      NoFileOpenedException - if a file is not opened.
      WrongArgumentsCountException - if the arguments count is incorrect.
